1. Introduction

Welcome to LightCowcontrol . Your privacy is critically important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information. By using the App, you consent to the practices described in this policy.

This Privacy Policy is publicly accessible at: [Insert Active Public URL Here]

2. Data Collection and Usage

We collect and use only the necessary personal data required to operate and improve the App. The types of data collected include:

User Credentials: Such as email addresses and passwords (stored securely).

Activity Logs: To monitor app usage, improve performance, and ensure security.

Device Information: Includes device model, operating system version, and unique identifiers for analytics and troubleshooting.

How We Use Your Data:

To provide and improve the functionality of the App.

To enhance security and prevent fraud.

To comply with legal obligations where required.

We do not sell or share your data with third parties without your explicit consent, except as required by law.

3. Data Security Measures

We implement industry-standard security measures to protect user data, including encryption, access controls, and regular security audits. However, users are responsible for safeguarding their accounts and should avoid sharing login credentials.

4. Data Retention and Deletion Policy

We retain user data only for as long as necessary to provide the App’s services and comply with legal obligations. Users can request data deletion by contacting us at assolaange777@gmail.com. Once a deletion request is processed, data will be permanently removed from our servers.

5. Intellectual Property Rights

All intellectual property related to LightCowcontrol, including but not limited to the app’s design, source code, and branding, is owned solely by Lightgroup.

Prohibited Actions:

Unauthorized Duplication or Access to Source Code: Reverse engineering or accessing the source code without permission is strictly prohibited.

False Ownership Claims: Claiming ownership of the App’s intellectual property without authorization is prohibited.

Malicious Publicity: Engaging in intentionally damaging publicity against the App is strictly prohibited.

6. Limitation of Liability

The App is provided "as-is" without warranties of any kind. We are not liable for any damages arising from the use of the App except as explicitly stated in this policy.

7. Legal Jurisdiction

This Privacy Policy is governed by the laws of Cameroon. Any disputes related to this policy or the App will be resolved exclusively in the courts of MTN.

8. Changes to the Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. Significant changes will be communicated via in-app notifications or email.

